{"word":"Jeroboam","slug":"jeroboam","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Jeroboam</b> <a href=\"#/H3379\">H3379</a> <br/> 1. First king of Israel after the revolt<br/> - Promoted by Solomon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=11&verse=28'>1Ki 11:28</a> <br/> - Ahijah's prophecy concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=11&verse=39'>1Ki 11:39</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=14&verse=16'>1Ki 14:16</a> <br/> - Flees to Egypt to escape from Solomon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=11&verse=40'>1Ki 11:40</a> <br/> - Recalled from Egypt by the ten tribes on account of disaffection toward Rehoboam, and made king<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=12&verse=20'>1Ki 12:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=10&verse=19'>2Ch 10:19</a> <br/> - Subverts the religion of Moses<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=12&verse=33'>1Ki 12:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=13&verse=34'>1Ki 13:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=14&verse=9'>1Ki 14:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=14&verse=16'>1Ki 14:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=16&verse=2'>1Ki 16:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=16&verse=26'>1Ki 16:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=16&verse=31'>1Ki 16:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=11&verse=14'>2Ch 11:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=13&verse=9'>2Ch 13:9</a> <br/> - Hand of, paralyzed<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=13&verse=10'>1Ki 13:10</a> <br/> - His wife sent to consult the prophet Ahijah concerning her child<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=14&verse=18'>1Ki 14:18</a> <br/> - His wars with Rehoboam<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=14&verse=19'>1Ki 14:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=14&verse=30'>1Ki 14:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=15&verse=6'>1Ki 15:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=11&verse=4'>2Ch 11:4</a> <br/> - His war with Abijah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=15&verse=7'>1Ki 15:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=13'>2Ch 13</a> <br/> - Death of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=14&verse=20'>1Ki 14:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=13&verse=20'>2Ch 13:20</a> <br/> 2. King of Israel<br/> - Successor to Jehoash<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=14&verse=16'>2Ki 14:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=14&verse=23'>2Ki 14:23</a> <br/> - Makes conquest of Hamath and Damascus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=14&verse=28'>2Ki 14:28</a> <br/> - Wicked reign of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=14&verse=24'>2Ki 14:24</a> <br/> - Prophecies concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=7&verse=13'>Amo 7:13</a> <br/> - Death of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=14&verse=29'>2Ki 14:29</a> <br/> - Genealogies written during his reign<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=5&verse=17'>1Ch 5:17</a> "}]}